          <li><b>Legitimate interest</b></li></li>
          <br>
          <p>  This is where the Company has a legitimate reason to process your data provided it is reasonable and does not go against what you would reasonably expect from us. Where the Company has relied on a legitimate interest to process your personal data our legitimate interests is/are as follows:</p>
